707142f-a.text:
Utica Ave., east side, looking east, between Farragut Road and Folger Place, showing the Serota Bros., coal pockets and beyond it the farmhouse of Johannes Ditmars, at the S.W. corner of King's Highway and Farragut Road.
March 1925
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
